cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use GoldenExperience, cite the negative-result paper below and do not describe this
  version as an approved cross-model serving speedup.
title: "GoldenExperience: Fail-Closed Cross-Model KV Cache Research"
type: software
abstract: >-
  GoldenExperience implements an auditable cross-model KV-cache translation and serving
  framework for vLLM, LMCache MP, and Mooncake Store. The publication-v5 Qwen3-4B to Qwen3-8B
  full-prefix transport fails its registered method-development safety gate; later calibration,
  validation, sealed, and runtime stages remain blocked.
authors:
  - name: "GoldenExperience Contributors"
repository-code: "https://github.com/XuTianle0101/GoldenExperience"
url: "https://github.com/XuTianle0101/GoldenExperience"
license: Apache-2.0
version: 0.1.0
date-released: 2026-07-13
keywords:
  - KV cache
  - cross-model reuse
  - language-model serving
  - negative results
  - reproducibility
preferred-citation:
  type: article
  title: "Can KV Caches Cross Model Scales? A Fail-Closed Evaluation of Qwen3 Prefix Translation"
  authors:
    - name: "GoldenExperience Contributors"
  year: 2026
  url: "https://github.com/XuTianle0101/GoldenExperience/blob/main/paper/paper.md"
